node.text:
Some people search their whole lives for great friends, 
& some great friends... make you search! 
.
We've kept busy during this lock down with yoga, trivia, dance classes, coffee times, games, & getting to know each other.  You learn more about a person in the months spent onboard together 24/7 than years put into building the same lifelong friendships on land.  So when these friends leave, their absence is felt like a hole in the heart. 

But in true QuaranTeam style, my pals didn't go quietly.  They left behind a scavenger hunt full of memories, a lot of laughter and a ton of tears.
Dr. Seuss said it best:
“Don’t cry because it’s over. Smile because it happened.”
Thank you for the countless smiles.  Thank you for being "family".
.

.
Thank you @celebrityedge & @celebritycruises for the gorgeous crew tour in St. Maarten! The Edge team arranged transportation & our own private beach for 150 of our crew. More tours & opportunities to come!
This was the first time I've been ashore since joining this contract & it was the perfect way to wade back in!
.
